name: The Strange Occurrences at 221 Elm St, Apartment 11B
name_original: The Strange Occurrences at 221 Elm St, Apartment 11B
description:
READ PLEASE

We didn't finish in time so all you can do is walk around, open doors and stuff. The win and lose condition is not done.

This was made for Extra Spoopy Game Jam #1 but we failed to submit in time by minutes. :(

We will be jamming until the end of October so if you feel so inclined, we'd love it if you checked back on or after Halloween night to play a more complete version of the game.
